            "icon": "lightning_bolt",
            "row_content": "<p>Most Nam Nam goodies (like brittles, popcorn, and candies) stay perfectly fresh for <strong>6–9 months</strong> when stored in a cool, dry place -no refrigeration needed. Each pack has a “Best Before” date mentioned on it for your peace of mind.</p>",
